title: Episode 08
description:
Radio Rental...Returns

Welcome to Radio Rental, a mysterious video rental store with a VHS tape collection of TRUE scary stories, narrated by the people who experienced them.

On today’s tapes…

>> Wrong Mom
A young girl goes to the grocery store... but who’s pushing the cart?

 >> Jump Cut
He’s living life. Then... cut to: next scene.
